<%- include('partials/header') %>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);
    padding: 70px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  [data-theme="dark"] .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #020617 0%, #0F172A 100%); }
  .page-hero-icon {
    width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 20px;
    background: rgba(0,102,255,0.15);
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 18px; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: #FFFFFF; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .page-content { padding: 56px 0; background: var(--bg-body); }
  .content-wrapper { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  
  .policy-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: clamp(20px, 4vw, 32px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  .policy-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .policy-card h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.3rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .policy-card h2 i { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .policy-card p { color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  .policy-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .policy-card ul li {
    padding: 8px 0; color: var(--text-body); font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.6; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px;
  }
  .policy-card ul li i { color: var(--success); margin-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  
  .highlight-box {
    background: var(--primary-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,102,255,0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .highlight-box i { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .highlight-box span { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 48px 0; }
    .page-hero-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .page-content { padding: 36px 0; }
    .policy-card { padding: 20px; }
    .policy-card p { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .policy-card ul li { font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .highlight-box { padding: 14px 16px; }
  }
</style>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck-fast"></i></div>
  <h1 class="page-hero-title">Shipping Policy</h1>
</div>

<div class="page-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Where We Ship</h2>
        <p>ShopNest proudly ships to customers worldwide. We work with reliable international carriers to ensure your orders reach you safely, no matter where you are.</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">
          <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
          <span>We ship to over 50+ countries including US, UK, Canada, Australia, Europe, Asia, and more.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Processing Time</h2>
        <p>All orders are processed within <strong>1-3 business days</strong> after payment confirmation. You will receive a confirmation email with your order details once your order is placed.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Order processing: 1-3 business days</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Order cutoff time: 5:00 PM (GMT)</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Weekend orders processed on Monday</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-shipping-fast"></i> Shipping Times & Rates</h2>
        <p>Shipping times vary depending on your location and the shipping method selected at checkout. Below are our estimated delivery timeframes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> <strong>Standard Shipping:</strong> 7-21 business days</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on your order and location</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Free shipping is available on orders meeting our threshold amount</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Tracking information is provided once your order ships</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-search-location"></i> Tracking Your Order</h2>
        <p>Once your order ships, you will receive a tracking number via email. You can track your order anytime by visiting our <a href="/track" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;">Track Order</a> page and entering your tracking number.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="policy-card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Important Notes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Delivery times are estimates and may vary due to customs clearance, weather conditions, or carrier delays.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Customers are responsible for any customs duties or import taxes that may apply.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Please ensure your shipping address is correct. We are not responsible for orders shipped to incorrect addresses.</li>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> If your package is marked as delivered but you haven't received it, please check with neighbors or your local post office first.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>